node.text:
Who’s ready for RedBud⁉️ Lot B is overrated so we’re taking the party to Lot C this year. Come join me at the @redbull hospitality for a kick back on Friday. I’m going to be hanging out, signing autographs, playing games and sharing stories with you guys. This isn’t an autograph line, but a hangout. First 100 people to Gate 4 will get a wristband. Let’s celebrate the USA 🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸

@redbullusa @redbullmotorsports
